 Vegemite as it doesn't emulsify well with the butter. You can find savoury yeast spreads in the international aisle of most major supermarkets.","<strong>Gluten free mini cheese scones:<\/strong> replace the plain flour and baking powder with gluten free flour and gluten free baking powder. Some yeast spreads may contain traces of wheat or gluten. Please check the labels of your products to ensure they are gluten free."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","30m","24 portions"]}